1
Inviting you to use the glimble app.
In certain cases, we may use your contact information to send you an invitation to use our glimble app via email. If we have already received your electronic contact details in connection with the sale of one of our similar products or services and you have not previously objected to unsolicited communications from us, you will be regarded as an existing customer and we will send the invitation on the basis of our legitimate interest (as stated opposite). In other cases, you will be considered a new customer and we will send the invitation on the basis of your prior consent (as mentioned opposite). In both cases, we offer you the opportunity to object to the (further) use of your electronic contact details. Objection can be made (in addition to the manner described in the relevant email) by contacting us as described in this privacy statement.
